<div class="container">
  <p>
    In a <%- link('separate post', { href: '/posts/last-fm' }) %>, you can peruse my top albums and artists for various timeframes, all going back from the present. For example, you can view my top listens from the last 3 months. It's been fascinating to observe how my listening habits have evolved over time, as well as how they've remained consistent.
  </p>
